snippet.title: How Amber Heard FAILED to "make" Johnny Depp Hit Her
snippet.description:
This is a follow-up Part 2 of my video "Narcissistic Abuse Recorded."
ONE CORRECTION: Amber threw the glass vodka bottle at Johnny in Australia because Johnny asked her for a post-nuptial agreement. Not because of Elon Musk, although she asked the security folks at the penthouse building to let her "friend Elon" use the parking garage, etc. shortly after that incident.  
Here is a link to Adam Waldman'(Depp's lawyer)'s statement discussing that and MUCH more.
https://www.courthousenews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/DeppHeard.pdf
Special thanks goes out to @ThatBrianFella on Twitter, who shed more light upon that insidious video  Amber Heard tried to use against Johnny Depp.  Here is a link to Brian's video under his YouTube handle "Incredibly Average."
Amber Heard & Johnny Depp abuse claims(and the lies not talked about?)
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mN1B-H7i0nE&t=510s

The one picture with the remote in Amber's hand circled in red, appears in "Narcissistic Abuse Recorded" for the first time at 1:00.
